{"tid":1790413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［今日要置頂，好重要要上熱門］今晚荔枝角要人！！！！！","createTime":"2019-12-20T03:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T13:50:23.000Z","uid":113415,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2cc2ea1efa753ff96c5f235a1d1a9421660ab3","tid":1790413,"uid":113415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽講今次集會係有荔枝角收押所手足係裡面寫信出黎，想大家係聖誕期間係監獄出面搞個集會聲援佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以大家一定要到，仲要今次係監獄出面集會都有不反喎！尤其係和理非！除左寫聖誕卡，和理非有更多實際行動要做！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同時今日探完一位手足朋友，佢話大家支持佢地，佢地真係好感動好開心。但記得要小心安全，佢想大家聲援，唔係想大家入埋黎，因為入面真係唔好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【和你撐手足】荔枝角聲援手足集會<br />\n<br />\n日期：20/12/2019(五)<br />\n時間：8:00pm開始<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所外（九龍蝴蝶谷道5號）<br />\n已取得不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n反修例運動至今逾6000人被捕，現有約80位手足被拒保釋還柙中。荔枝角收押所的手足需要我們的支持，約定你參與「和你撐手足」荔枝角集會，讓手足們知道香港人不會讓他們孤單。<br />\n<br />\n十二月二十日，和你撐手足！！！<br />\n<br />\n主辦團體：<br />\n邵家臻立法會議員辦事處<br />\n張超雄立法會議員辦事處<br />\n社會民主連線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.200856493433676/1244770899042225?type=3&amp;sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fphotos%2Fa.200856493433676%2F1244770899042225%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3D1&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5SC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=8716cd43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.200856493433676/1244770899042225?type=3&amp;sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100226174720726/posts/154908259252517?substory_index=0&amp;sfns=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100226174720726%2Fposts%2F154908259252517%3Fsubstory_index%3D0%26sfns%3D&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5SC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=a32dc5f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl